comment:
* An event recorded by ConnectivityService when there is a change in the default network.
 * {@hide}

variables.name: creationTimeMs
variables.comment: The creation time in milliseconds of this DefaultNetworkEvent.

variables.name: netId
variables.comment: The network ID of the network or NETID_UNSET if none.

variables.name: transports
variables.comment: The list of transport types, as defined in NetworkCapabilities.java.

variables.name: previousTransports
variables.comment: The list of transport types of the last previous default network.

variables.name: ipv4
variables.comment: Whether the network has IPv4/IPv6 connectivity.

variables.name: initialScore
variables.comment: The initial network score when this network became the default network.

variables.name: finalScore
variables.comment: The initial network score when this network stopped being the default network.

variables.name: durationMs
variables.comment: The total duration in milliseconds this network was the default network.

variables.name: validatedMs
variables.comment: The total duration in milliseconds this network was the default network and was validated.

methods.name: public void updateDuration(long timeMs)
methods.comment: Update the durationMs of this DefaultNetworkEvent for the given current time.
